commit message:
Update v1.0.5

Added new settings allowing for toggling corners.

Settings tweak (minor)

Now it tells the user what the radius is in dp

Layout changes

Changed settings layout by a little bit. Added 4dp more margin on
checkbox trCB

Settings Fix

Fixed bug with textview reading 2dp lower

Apache + Boot Fix

Licensed under Apache 2.0 and fixed launching upon boot.

Expanded Desktop & YouTube Support

Auto refresh all corners every 500ms

Update v1.7.0

- YouTube fullscreen bug fixed
- Support added for expanded desktop
- New icon!
- Settings animation removed

Update v1.8.0

Battery + RAM improved
Orientation Listening is awesome
Animation added back

Update v1.9.0

- Settings refreshes TextView as slider is slid
- Source code has extra code for algorithmic corners (disabled by
default)

Update 1.9.5

Lock screen support added
Touch underneath corners

Update v2.0.0

Added option to not overlap notifications

Update v2.5.0

Major breakthrough fixing bug with fullscreen video players. Eliminates
need for orientation change listening.

Update v2.6.0.0

Added ability to display above colored status bars

Update v3.0.0

Redesigned Settings UI with standard Android settings.
